Use the listed types of standard creative benchmarking strategies

01:16:06.000 --> 01:16:11.000
to create a concept of event promotion of your company's brand.

01:16:12.000 --> 01:16:17.000
It is always difficult to switch from a textbook example to a real one.

01:16:17.000 --> 01:16:21.000
But we will remember that Caterpillar is also a real brand.

01:16:21.000 --> 01:16:26.000
If you can create some interesting creative ideas

01:16:26.000 --> 01:16:29.000
based on benchmarking technology for your company,

01:16:29.000 --> 01:16:32.000
you can use this experience tomorrow.

01:16:41.000 --> 01:16:42.000
Thank you.
